# Hugo build output & cache
/public/
/resources/_gen/
.hugo_build.lock

# Hugo module lockfile — regenerated on every `hugo mod get` and changes
# constantly with the unpinned blog-content module. CI regenerates in-place.
/go.sum

# Module-owned content (comes from github.com/dzarlax/blog-content at build
# time). Section _index.md files are tracked; everything below them is not.
# If a stray article appears here from a legacy `bin/sync-content.sh` run,
# it's ignored — keeps the repo from drifting back to the old flow.
/content/articles/*/
/content/tags/*/

# OS
.DS_Store
